  <brief_title>Study to Evaluate Safety and Immunologic Biomarker of Rapamune in Patients With Stable Renal Transplant Recipient</brief_title>
  <official_title>Investigation of the Safety and Immunologic Biomarker After Conversion From Calcineurin Inhibitor to Rapamune in Stable Renal Transplant Recipient</official_title>
