  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. Renal transplant recipient who has passed at least 10 years

          2. No acute rejection episode during the previous 6 months

          3. No change of prescription of immune suppressants

          4. Normal allograft function (MDRD eGFR &gt; 80 mL/min/1.73 m2)

          5. Change of allograft function less than 10 % of baseline value durant the previous 1
             year

          6. No proteinuria and hematuria

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. Patients who donut want to participate in this study

          2. Patients who should continue immune suppressant due to another cause (e/g combined
             autoimmune disease)
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
